setDisableUnauthorizedButtons

public void setDisableUnauthorizedButtons(Boolean disableUnauthorizedButtons)
Description copied from interface: ServicePanelDef
[OPTIONAL] Assigns a new value to the disableUnauthorizedButtons. This property indicates whether the buttons the user is not authorized to press will be disabled or will be enabled and a message will be displayed when they are pressed. This defaults to false.
